{"title":"计算机网络","uid":"293c17b4d2a4292133cc4d1ffd7f8725","slug":"计算机网络","date":"2023-04-04T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-04-06T07:32:58.992Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/计算机网络.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"计算机网络\"><a href=\"#计算机网络\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"计算机网络\"></a>计算机网络</h1><p>最近复习计网，看的是<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1c4411d7jb?p=8&spm_id_from=pageDriver&vd_source=a12f9c06a232cb2697b9043d3998ebcf\">1.6 计算机网络体系结构（2）—分层的必要性_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a>，讲的很好。</p>\n<p>参考教材是王道的，这里记录了一些补充知识点。</p>\n<h2 id=\"体系结构\"><a href=\"#体系结构\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"体系结构\"></a>体系结构</h2><h3 id=\"网络分层的必要性：\"><a href=\"#网络分层的必要性：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"网络分层的必要性：\"></a>网络分层的必要性：</h3><ul>\n<li><p>数据链路层</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230318120323897.png\" alt=\"image-20230318120323897\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>网络层</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230318120409934.png\" alt=\"image-20230318120409934\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>运输层</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230318121018883.png\" alt=\"image-20230318121018883\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>应用层</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230318121125915.png\" alt=\"image-20230318121125915\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230318171559887.png\" alt=\"image-20230318171559887\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230318165048500.png\" alt=\"image-20230318165048500\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"时延问题\"><a href=\"#时延问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"时延问题\"></a>时延问题</h3><p><img src=\"/img/image-20230318210632985.png\" alt=\"image-20230318210632985\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"数据链路层\"><a href=\"#数据链路层\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"数据链路层\"></a>数据链路层</h2><h3 id=\"检错-循环冗余-CRC\"><a href=\"#检错-循环冗余-CRC\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"检错-循环冗余 CRC\"></a>检错-循环冗余 CRC</h3><p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319120001875.png\" alt=\"image-20230319120001875\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319120047180.png\" alt=\"image-20230319120047180\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"可靠传输的实现机制\"><a href=\"#可靠传输的实现机制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"可靠传输的实现机制\"></a>可靠传输的实现机制</h3><h4 id=\"停止-等待协议-SW\"><a href=\"#停止-等待协议-SW\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"停止-等待协议 SW\"></a>停止-等待协议 SW</h4><p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319124115187.png\" alt=\"image-20230319124115187\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"回退-N\"><a href=\"#回退-N\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"回退 N\"></a>回退 N</h4><p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319131135300.png\" alt=\"image-20230319131135300\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"选择重传-SR\"><a href=\"#选择重传-SR\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"选择重传 SR\"></a>选择重传 SR</h4><p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319132144488.png\" alt=\"image-20230319132144488\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"PPP-协议\"><a href=\"#PPP-协议\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"PPP 协议\"></a>PPP 协议</h3><ul>\n<li>怎么实现透明传输</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319140040854.png\" alt=\"image-20230319140040854\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319140144190.png\" alt=\"image-20230319140144190\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>工作状态</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319140711251.png\" alt=\"image-20230319140711251\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"MAC-地址-IP-地址和-ARP-协议\"><a href=\"#MAC-地址-IP-地址和-ARP-协议\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"MAC 地址 IP 地址和 ARP 协议\"></a>MAC 地址 IP 地址和 ARP 协议</h3><p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319195505609.png\" alt=\"image-20230319195505609\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"集线器和交换机\"><a href=\"#集线器和交换机\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"集线器和交换机\"></a>集线器和交换机</h3><p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319201222082.png\" alt=\"image-20230319201222082\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319202433915.png\" alt=\"image-20230319202433915\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"vlan\"><a href=\"#vlan\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"vlan\"></a>vlan</h3><p>vlan 可以隔离广播域</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319210834417.png\" alt=\"image-20230319210834417\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"网络层\"><a href=\"#网络层\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"网络层\"></a>网络层</h2><h3 id=\"虚电路和数据报\"><a href=\"#虚电路和数据报\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"虚电路和数据报\"></a>虚电路和数据报</h3><p><img src=\"/img/image-20230319222056253.png\" alt=\"image-20230319222056253\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"IPV4-地址的三个阶段\"><a href=\"#IPV4-地址的三个阶段\" class=\"headerlink\" title=